## **What is One-on-One Private Firearm Instruction?**

One-on-One Private Instruction at Live Fire Instruction offers personalized, sixty-minute coaching sessions tailored to the specific goals of individual shooters in Northern Virginia. Operating out of the NRA National Range in Fairfax, these private lessons are ideal for both absolute beginners seeking a low-pressure introduction and experienced shooters looking to refine advanced techniques. Each session provides a practical, working understanding of shooting fundamentals, including sight alignment, trigger press, and recoil management. Instructors adapt the curriculum in real-time to address the student's unique equipment needs and skill level, ensuring maximum progress in a short timeframe. Additional lessons build upon these foundations by introducing defensive pistol drills and complex marksmanship skills. Private instruction is an efficient way to gain confidence and technical proficiency under the direct supervision of NRA-certified experts, whether training for personal protection, competitive shooting, or general recreational firearm safety and responsible ownership.

## **Sign up today for this course.**

If you have any questions, call [1-571-210-5651](tel:15712105651), or email at [class@livefireinstruction.com](mailto:class@livefireinstruction.com)
